own (rugby league)|Lou Brown]] 2, S Crewther\n| con1 = S Crewther\n| pen1 =\n| try2 =\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Carlaw Park 2\n| attendance =\n| referee = L Bull\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 23 May\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Marist\n| score = 18-0\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Marist and City Win\n| page =13\n| work= [[The New Zealand Herald]] |volume=LXII |issue=19026\n| date = 1925-05-25\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19250525.2.131.1\n| accessdate = 2019-09-11}}</ref>\n| away = Newton\n| try1 = [[Hec Brisbane]] 2, Malloy, [[Arthur Singe]]\n| con1 = P Gregory 2\n| pen1 = P Gregory\n| try2 =\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Auckland Domain\n| attendance =\n| referee = Hill\n}}\n\n======Round 6======\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 30 May\n| time = 3:00\n| home = City\n| score = 9-7\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Leaders' Great Contest/Marist Beaten By City\n| page = 12\n| work= [[The New Zealand Herald]] |volume=LXII |issue=19032\n| date = 1925-06-01\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19250601.2.139.6\n| accessdate = 2019-09-11}}</ref>\n| away = Marist\n| try1 = Mitchell\n| con1 = Sandham\n| pen1 = Sandham\n| drop1 = [[Ben Davidson (rugby league)|Ben Davidson]]\n| try2 = [[Jack Kirwan (rugby league)|Jack Kirwan]]\n| con2 = [[Charles Gregory (rugby league)|Charles Gregory]]\n| pen2 = [[Charles Gregory (rugby league)|Charles Gregory]]\n| stadium = Carlaw Park 1\n| attendance = 12500\n| referee = W Ripley\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 30 May\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Ponsonby\n| score = 18-6\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Leaders' Great Contest\n| page = 12\n| work= [[The New Zealand Herald]] |volume=LXII |issue=19032\n| date = 1925-06-01\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19250601.2.139.6\n| accessdate = 2019-09-11}}</ref>\n| away = Athletic\n| try1 = [[Frank Delgrosso]], A Payne, [[Ivan Littlewood]], [[Hector Cole]]\n| con1 =\n| pen1 = [[Frank Del