 of Owen Marshall, Counselor at Law episodes|To Keep and Bear Arms]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Bob Newhart Show]]''\n| Dave\n| Episode: \"[[List of The Bob Newhart Show episodes|Sorry, Wrong Mother]]\"\n|-\n| rowspan=10|1975\n| ''[[Movin' On (TV series)|Movin' On]]''\n| Casey\n| Episode: \"Landslide\"\n|-\n| ''[[Mannix]]''\n| Cliff Elgin\n| Episode: \"[[List of Mannix episodes#Season 8|Hardball]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Bob Crane Show]]''\n| Hornbeck\n| Episode: \"Son of the Campus Capers\"\n|-\n| ''[[Petrocelli]]''\n| John Oleson\n| Episode: \"Chain of Command\"\n|-\n| ''[[Barnaby Jones]]''\n| Joe Rockwell\n| Episode: \"[[List of Barnaby Jones episodes|The Price of Terror]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Streets of San Francisco]]''\n| John 'Johnny' Steiner\n| Episode: \"[[List of The Streets of San Francisco episodes|Murder by Proxy]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Night That Panicked America]]''\n| Walter Wingate\n| [[Television film|TV  film]]\n|-\n| ''[[The Mary Tyler Moore Show]]''\n| Reverend Chatfield\n| Episode: \"[[List of The Mary Tyler Moore Show episodes#Season Six 1975\u20131976|Ted's Wedding]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Rookies]]''\n| Hap Dawson\n| Episode: \"[[List of The Rookies episodes|Reluctant Hero]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[Rhoda]]''\n| Vince Mazuma / Jerry Blocker\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1976\n| ''[[Starsky & Hutch]]''\n| Tom Cole\n| Episode:  \"[[List of Starsky & Hutch episodes#Season 1 (1975\u201376)|The Hostages]]\"\n|-\n| ''[[Phyllis (TV series)|Phyllis]]''\n| Paul Jameson\n| Episode: \"[[List of Phyllis episodes|The New Job]]\"\n|-\n| 1977\u20131984\n| ''[[Three's Company]]''\n| [[Jack Tripper]]\n| Lead role (174 episodes)\n|-\n| 1977\n| ''[[Tattletales]]''\n| Himself\n| Panelist\n|-\n| 1977, 1983\n| ''[[The Love Boat]]''\n| Dale Riley/Reinhardt / Ben Cummins\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=3|1978\n| ''[[$100,000 Pyramid|$25,000 Pyramid]]''\n| Himself\n| Panelist\n|-\n| ''[[Ringo (1978 film)|Ringo]]''\n| Marty\n| TV film\n|-\n| ''Leave Yesterday Behind''\n| Paul Stallings\n| TV film\n|-\n| 1979\n| 